Recipe is per serving of noodles.

Sauce:
- 3 cloves garlic
- 1tbsp oyster sauce
- 2tsp soy sauce
- 2tsp sesame oil
- 2tsp rice vinegar
- 2tsp black papper

1/2 green cabbage, chopped
3 cloves minced garlic
Stir fry the cabbage 5min

Udon noodles, soaked in boiling water about 2 minutes

Optionally, add sliced tofu at this point
Add garlic to stirfry, stir fry 3min more
Add udon
Add sauce
Cook 1 minute with sauce
Mess forth.
